Q.notification - small library for JavaScript to show popups notification

(Optional) needs Q.opacity lib

Using:
Q.notification.show(text)

text: string (support html tags)
	message on popup

Example:

<a onclick="Q.notification.show("ch0nada xD");">its popup...chVe</a>

OR

<a onclick="Q.notification.show("ch0nada xD<br /><b>new line</b>");">its popup...with html tags</a>